<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>The Maestro - Device Authorized</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 50px 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        color: white;
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        padding: 40px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        color: #4ade80;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .success-icon {
        font-size: 4rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .highlight {
        background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.2);
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #4ade80;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="success-icon">âœ…</div>
      <h1>Device Authorized!</h1>
      <p>You have successfully authorized your device to access The Maestro.</p>
      
      <div class="highlight">
        <strong>Your terminal session is now authenticated!</strong>
      </div>
      
      <p>You can now close this browser tab and return to your terminal.</p>
      <p>The CLI will automatically continue with your authenticated session.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>